00 Specifications] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120321232627/http://www.aer.ita.br/~bmattos/mundo/airliner/fo100.htm |date=2012-03-21 }}  ''aer.ita.br.'' Retrieved: 29 January 2012.\n</ref>\n\n==See also==\n{{aircontent\n|see also=\n|related=\n* [[Fokker 70]]\n|similar aircraft=\n* [[Airbus A220]]\n* [[Airbus A318]]\n* [[British Aerospace 146]]\n* [[Boeing 717]]\n* [[Bombardier CRJ700 series|Bombardier CRJ1000]]\n* [[Embraer E-Jet family|Embraer E-190/195]]\n* [[Fairchild Dornier 728 family]]\n* [[Sukhoi Superjet 100]]\n* [[Tupolev Tu-334]]\n|lists=\n* [[List of jet airliners]]\n* [[List of civil aircraft]]\n}}\n\n\n==References==\n===Citations===\n{{reflist|2}}\n\n===Bibliography===\n{{refbegin}}\n* Taylor, Michael J. H. '''Brassey's World Aircraft & Systems Directory.'' London: Brassey's, 1996. {{ISBN|1-85753-198-1}}.\n{{refend}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commonscat-inline|Fokker 100}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20100405081233/http://www.flyfokker.com/Stork/18515/FF_F100.html Fokker 100 page on manufacturer's site]\n* [http://www.fokkerservices.com/page.html?ch=DEF&id=7307 Future100 Executive Jet] and [http://www.fokkerservices.com/page.html?id=5714 operators pages on FokkerServices.com]\n* [http://www.rekkof.nl/ Rekkof Project]\n* [http://www.planepictures.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=268&start=0&postdays=0&postorder=asc&highlight=&sid=0bba7879d2c01b91d2973fd89a23301c Rekkof : Fokker 100NG]{{dead link|date=October 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}\n* [http://www.airliners.net/info/stats.main?id=221 Fokker 100 info]\n\n{{Fokker aircraft}}\n\n[[Category:1980s Dutch airliners]]\n[[Category:Fokker aircraft|100]]\n[[Category:Twinjets]]\n[[Category:T-tail aircraft]]\n[[Category:Aircraft first flown in 1986]]\n[[Category:Low-wing aircraft]]\n", "name_user": "Emanresucamit", "label": "safe", "comment": "removed Bek Air as an operational airline because their license was revoked after last year's crash", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/